@node Main "The ARexx Interface Designer"

@{fg shine}The ARexx Interface Designer@{fg text}

Beginning with V2.0, EasyRexx offers an intuitive method of designing your ARexx interface (also called the 'Designer' in this documentation).  With this utility you can design the entire interface in a very intuitive way without any programming at all.

