@{fg shine}Arguments@{fg text}
@{u}data@{uu}
Type of information to return.  Must be one of the following: COMMANDLIST, AUTHOR, COPYRIGHT, VERSION or LASTERROR.

@{fg shine}Description@{fg text}
This command will be present for all applications that use the easyrexx.library and it is handled entirely by the library. The purpose of this command is to return information about the application to the user.

@{fg shine}Returns@{fg text}
COMMANDLIST
Returns a list (string) of all commands known to your application (internal commands will be listed at the beginning of the list).

AUTHOR
Returns the name of author of the application.

COPYRIGHT
