@node arexx_requestfile "REQUESTFILE"

@{fg shine}Synopsis@{fg text}
REQUESTFILE @{u}title@{uu} @{u}file@{uu} [SAVE] [DRAWERS] [NOICONS]

@{fg shine}Arguments@{fg text}
@{u}title@{uu}
File requester title

@{u}file@{uu}
Path and name of pre-selected file.

SAVE
The file requester save mode.  The background will be black and no doubleclicking on filenames will be allowed.  Use only for files that will be saved.

DRAWERS
The file requester will display drawers only.

NOICONS
No .info files will be displayed in the file requester.

@{fg shine}Description@{fg text}
Displays a file requester in which the user may select a file.

@{fg shine}Returns@{fg text}
An empty string if the user cancelled the requester.  Any other string will indicate what file the user selected or entered.

@{fg shine}Examples@{fg text}
REQUESTFILE '"Open file" "ram:test" NOICONS'
REQUESTFILE '"Save file" "ram:test" SAVE'
REQUESTFILE '"Select drawer" "ram:env" DRAWERS'
@endnode

