SETATTR  @{u}variable@{uu}=@{u}value@{uu} [ @{u}variable@{uu}= @{u}value@{uu} ...]

@{fg shine}Arguments@{fg text}
@{u}value@{uu} is the new value of the AREXX Interface variable.  

@{u}variable@{uu} must be one of the following:

ALWAYS
State of Always checkgadget (0 or 1).

KEYWORD
State of Keyword checkgadget (0 or 1).

MULTIPLE
State of Multiple checkgadget (0 or 1).

NUMBER
State of Number checkgadget (0 or 1).

SWITCH
State of Switch checkgadget (0 or 1).

TOGGLE
State of Toggle checkgadget (0 or 1).

FINAL
State of Final checkgadget (0 or 1).

AUTHOR
Author string (string).

COPYRIGHT
Copyright string (string).

VERSION
Version string (string).

PORTNAME
Portname string (string).

MAIN
State of Main Code checkgadget (0 or 1).

AREXXHANDLER
State of AREXX Handler checkgadget (0 or 1).

TEMPLATES
State of Templates  checkgadget (0 or 1).

HANDLERTYPE
State of Handlertype (0 or 1).

MACRO
Which macro to rename.

MACRONAME
Name of new macro.

@{fg shine}Description@{fg text}
Sets the value of a variable from the AREXX Interface Designer.

@{fg shine}Examples@{fg text}
SETATTR 'VERSION="(C) 1995 Ketil Hunn"'
SETATTR 'ARGUMENT="force"'
SETATTR 'ALWAYS=1'
SETATTR 'FINAL=0 ALWAYS=1 AUTHOR="Ketil Hunn"'
SETATTR 'MACRO=1 MACRONAME="rexx:test.rexx"'
@endnode

